event.metrics.repository.name as RepoName,
event.metrics.sender.login as DeletedBy

select event.metrics.after as hashid, 
event.metrics.repository.name as repo, 
event.metrics.commits.committer.name[1] as committer, 
event.metrics.commits.message[1] as message,
event.metrics.repository.updated_at as time 
from test.git_json where event.repo == 'Github' and event.metrics.commits.committer.name[1] != ''  SETTINGS describe_extend_object_types=1;

targets.rawSql:
select event.metrics.pull_request.head.sha as hashid,
event.metrics.pull_request.state as pullreqstate, 
event.metrics.pull_request.created_at as time,
event.metrics.pull_request.user.login as author, 
event.metrics.pull_request.base.repo.owner.login as owner,
event.metrics.pull_request.body as message 
from test.git_json where event.repo == 'Github' and event.metrics.pull_request.head.sha !=''  SETTINGS describe_extend_object_types=1;
